name: Rêve Onirique
description:
I had a dream. I don’t remember everything and some details are still blurry in my memories.

Miyajima is one of my favorite place in Japan. This island in front of Hiroshima is well known for its great torii in the sea. I love to walk around and take a step back to have a global vision of places I visit.

With this pastel editing, I want to give a fantasy and dreamy aspect to my photos. Everything seems surrealist, like a vaporwave scene from old 80s anime.

[Fine Art print for collector]
